    <ul>
      <li>Display the Bingo gameboards with counters on all of the groups of 5.</li>
      <li><q>¿Cuál tarjeta piensan que este grupo volteó? ¿Cómo lo saben?</q> (They flipped over the card with the number 5. They covered up the groups with 5 things.)</li>
    </ul>
